  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23444186_1_605-630",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "605-630",
      "markText": "如果说，宗教、哲学给答案，艺术的终极关怀则是安慰。",
      "totalCount": 840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23444186&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=605&rangeEnd=630",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f607165bada47cfcad?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=605&rangeEnd=630"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23444186_12_6545-6595",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "6545-6595",
      "markText": "人生是很复杂的，并不是你给得多，人家就会感谢你；有时候你给得越多，只是让对方越觉得挫败，也越发怨恨。",
      "totalCount": 800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23444186&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6545&rangeEnd=6595",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f607165bada47cfcad?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6545&rangeEnd=6595"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23444186_2_2795-2838",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2795-2838",
      "markText": "中国民间的很多宗教是佛道合一，对一般人来讲，它不是用来赎罪的，只是用来帮助自己过日子。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23444186&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2795&rangeEnd=2838",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f607165bada47cfcad?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2795&rangeEnd=2838"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23444186_2_969-1055",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "969-1055",
      "markText": "《金瓶梅》写的就是“人”，写人的可笑、人的可怕，还有人的可悯。人的可笑在于，一天到晚就在做那一件事情；人的可怕则是，为了一点钱，就可以把人整死；人的可悲可悯，则是世事无常。",
